HSBC Alternative Buys Rest of 1540 Broadway in Manhattan’s Times Square

-- B y   R o s s   L a r s e n
-- 
2011-09-30T08:57:45Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-30/hsbc-alternative-buys-remainder-of-1540-broadway-in-manhattan.html
HSBC Alternative Investments Ltd.
and EDGE Fund Advisors bought the 51 percent of 1540 Broadway on
Manhattan’s Times Square that the HSBC unit didn’t already own.
Tenants include Yahoo! Inc., Pilsbury Winthrop Shaw Pittman LLP
and  China ’s Xinhua News Agency. No price was given.  To contact the reporter on this story:
